snippet.title: Premier Teaser officiel Avengers Doomsday
snippet.description:
Un teaser officiel Marvel pour Avengers 5 Doomsday sous forme de show de lumière dédié à Doctor Doom, un synopsis officiel partagé par Marvel dans le même événement qui explique l'histoire du film ainsi qu'une photo très mystérieuse posté par les frères Russo ! Fatalis qui reconstruit le Multivers en Battleworld, les anneaux de Shang-Chi créé par Doom, Kang le conquérant et j'en passe. Aujourd'hui on s'attaque aux nouvelles révélations autour de AVENGERS 5 DOOMSDAY. Une analyse complète, ultime, entre news, décryptage et théories ! Entre Doom et visage de Tony Stark, entre Kang et Fatalis. Bon visionnage 🌌🔮📺 (Abonnez-vous! Rejoignez l'aventure) 😇 Objectif 350.000 explorateurs !

📥 Mail pro : irosef@cultureg.eu
📩 Perso : sefiroxshow@gmail.com

🪐 Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/iro_sef/
🔥 Twitter : https://twitter.com/Iro_Sef

snippet.title: Bande-annonce officielle - OUI de Nadav Lapid (au cinéma le 17 septembre 2025)
snippet.description:
Découvrez la bande-annonce du nouveau film de Nadav Lapid 𝗢𝗨𝗜, qui va électriser la rentrée après avoir bousculé la Quinzaine des Cinéastes⚡️

𝗔𝘃𝗲𝗰 : Ariel Bronz, Efrat Dor, Naama Preis, Alexey Serebryakov

𝗦𝘆𝗻𝗼𝗽𝘀𝗶𝘀 : Israël au lendemain du 7 octobre. Y., musicien de jazz précaire, et sa femme Jasmine, danseuse, donnent leur art, leur âme et leur corps aux plus offrants, apportent plaisir et consolation à leur pays qui saigne. Bientôt, Y. se voit confier une mission de la plus haute importance : mettre en musique un nouvel hymne national.

𝗟𝗘 𝟭𝟳 𝗦𝗘𝗣𝗧𝗘𝗠𝗕𝗥𝗘 𝗔𝗨 𝗖𝗜𝗡𝗘𝗠𝗔

snippet.description:
— Attention Viewers ⚠️
— This is a Fan-Made Concept Trailer for:
— WEDNESDAY SEASON 3

— This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I’ve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support — now let’s dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. 🎬✨

— In this concept trailer for Wednesday Season 3, the story continues in the aftermath of Season 2 as Wednesday finds herself entangled in an even darker web of family curses and rising threats. Hidden beneath Grandmama Hester’s watch, Aunt Ophelia resurfaces with a chilling prophecy that Wednesday must die, while Professor Capri and Tyler rally a growing army of Hydes to wage war against Nevermore. At the same time, Enid has vanished into the wilderness, lost to her werewolf form, forcing Wednesday on a relentless search that blurs the line between friend and foe. As ancestral secrets unravel and enemies close in, Wednesday must confront not only the cult determined to claim her bloodline but also the possibility that destiny itself has marked her for destruction. With higher stakes, fractured alliances, and a promise of unrelenting darkness, this new chapter teases a battle where survival may demand the ultimate sacrifice.

snippet.title: Naruto - The Movie (2026) | The Destiny of a Ninja | Teaser Trailer 4K
snippet.description:
From the narrow streets of the Hidden Leaf Village to battles echoing through dark forests and forgotten mountains, this live-action adaptation brings back the first steps of Naruto and his companions in an era of challenges, pain, and hope.

🔹 The Heir’s Solitude – Young Naruto, marked by rejection, dreaming of becoming Hokage
🔹 Team 7 – The meeting with Sasuke and Sakura, and the arrival of Master Kakashi
🔹 The Chunin Exam – Deadly trials, clever strategies, and the arrival of new rivals
🔹 The Sound of Shadows – Orochimaru’s attack, the terror of the Sound Village, and the fight for survival
🔹 The Power of Friendship – Gaara’s awakening, the Kyuubi’s might, and the clash of ideals
🔹 The Departure – The bond between Naruto and Sasuke pushed to the limit in an unforgettable showdown

🔥 Naruto as you’ve never seen before. Real. Intense. Unforgettable.

👊 Heroes: Naruto Uzumaki, Sasuke Uchiha, Sakura Haruno, Kakashi Hatake, Rock Lee, Neji Hyuga, Hinata Hyuga, Gaara
⚔️ Villains: Orochimaru, Kabuto, Zabuza Momochi, Haku, Sound Ninjas, Uncontrolled Gaara
🌍 Iconic Locations: Hidden Leaf Village, Demon’s Bridge, Forest of Death, Chunin Exam Arena, Valley of the End

🎬 A visually reimagined era. But with the same ninja blood pulsing through generations.
The chakra awakens. The battle begins again.

📽️ Made with AI tools, extensive research, time, and dedication, in 4K resolution.

snippet.title: J'ai Triché avec une CAMÉRA en Bataille de Mob Minecraft !
snippet.description:
Aujourd'hui, c'est bataille de mobs ! Mais pour bien mettre en difficulté mon pote, j'ai uinstallé une caméra dans sa masion pour voir qu'est ce qu'il dessine !
Mail pour tout contact commercial : azpaztv@gmail.com
Mon Twitter : https://www.twitter.com/azpaztv
Mon Discord  + de nulcraft : https://discord.gg/EBPCS6YF9e
Merci pour les 500k road to 600k
Ce n'est pas Minecraft, Mais l'eau monte ou Minecraft, mais la lave monte, ou Survivre 100 jours dans Minecraft, ou tout type de défi dans Minecraft mais. Il s'agit d'un speedrun / Manhunt . Shorts
Dans cette vidéo Minecraft 1.20 (1.21 et non 1.19, 1.18 ou 1.17), je répondrai à toutes les questions que vous me poserez sans faire une seule exception. Il y a des questions embarrassantes, des questions intéressantes et beaucoup d'entre elles tout simplement stupides XD Cette vidéo est l'une de mes préférées que j'ai faites, alors profitez-en :)

Ce n'est pas Minecraft dans la vraie vie, pas l'édition éducative de Minecraft, pas Minecraft, mais en difficulté millionaire de riche. ou alors 7 façons de voler mes amis Cela répond à vos questions les plus litigieuses/absurdes.

Je vous aime tous beaucoup!

snippet.title: Fred again.. - Rooftop Live (Fede’s Roof, Naples)
snippet.description:
After a show i never quite know what to do. like you go from being filled with the most adreneline ever, to suddenly being like alone or basically alone. Often I just play songs im working on and jam on my keyboard to try ideas out to try n calm down and stuff, cos i cant really be social often. 

So when i saw fedde commenting on a post that he had a rooftop that overlooked the show i thought wow this could be like my dream afters. Just going straight up there and get to play songs on my ones and still get to see and feel the energy of the show as everyone leaves!

I played this whole set just to fedde and the beautiful nonna who also lives in this building. It was a lovely sight to look up occasionally and see them both there. Him dancing her sitting. Me a bit of both.

thankyou to Fede. 

directed by loose
shot by theo batterham & charlie hutchins
edit by charlie hutchins
recorded by tony friend
grade by tim smith
technical producer josh barnes
additional help from gianmarco
security by glen!
